Billion Dollar Secret



Company Summary
Xerium Technologies is a leading global manufacturer and supplier of two products used primarily in the production of paper: clothing and roll covers. The company, which operates around the world under a variety of brand names, owns a broad portfolio of patented and proprietary technologies to provide customers with tailored solutions and products integral to production, all designed to optimize performance and reduce operational costs.   

















 


















 







Xerium Technologies, Inc. (NYSE:XRM) :: Law360
































